SUB_W04_EVAR_SIUG_BASE_NORTHHARBOR_WORLD.text:
Baltasar's not a man to forget a grudge;
he's probably going to want to string
me up while he plays the hornpipe.

SUB_W04_EVAR_SIUG_PIRATESHIP_BIRD_QUEST_.text:
Yar, I suppose ya be but a victim;
'tis the fault of that slimy eel, Sigurd.
Here, cully. The treasure be yours.

SUB_W04_EVAR_SIUG_GHOSTSHIP_LASTBATTLE_1.text:
Ah. It seems the wish comes with a price;
I cannot be freed from my burden until I
bring down this fiend.
